001package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.processor.exception;
002
003import org.jetbrains.annotations.NotNull;
004
005/**
006 * Thrown when an exception occurs during processing
007 *
008 * @version 1.7.0
009 * @since 1.7.0
010 */
011public class ProcessorException extends RuntimeException {
012    /**
013     * Create a new ProcessorException
014     *
015     * @param cause The cause of the exception
016     */
017    public ProcessorException(@NotNull Exception cause) {
018        super("Error while processing:", cause);
019    }
020}
